fields.name: AccessResourcePath
fields.description: The resource path to get access relative to factory. Currently only empty string is supported which corresponds to the factory resource.

fields.name: ExpireTime
fields.description: Expiration time for the token. Maximum duration for the token is eight hours and by default the token will expire in eight hours.

fields.name: Permissions
fields.description: The string with permissions for Data Plane access. Currently only 'r' is supported which grants read only access.

fields.name: ProfileName
fields.description: The name of the profile. Currently only the default is supported. The default value is DefaultProfile.

fields.name: StartTime
fields.description: Start time for the token. If not specified the current time will be used.
